so sore as keeping safe Nerissa's ring.

1469
02:03:41,011 --> 02:03:49,020
The world was all before them

1470
02:03:49,103 --> 02:03:56,402
Ah

1471
02:03:56,486 --> 02:04:04,537
Where to choose their place of rest

1472
02:04:04,620 --> 02:04:11,586
Ah

1473
02:04:12,379 --> 02:04:16,216
And Providence their guide

1474
02:04:16,341 --> 02:04:20,095
They hand in hand

1475
02:04:20,178 --> 02:04:27,728
Took their wand'ring steps

1476
02:04:27,854 --> 02:04:31,775
And slow

1477
02:04:31,859 --> 02:04:35,904
Through Eden

1478
02:04:35,988 --> 02:04:43,121
Took their solitary way

1479
02:04:43,580 --> 02:04:49,085
Ah...

1480
02:05:50,402 --> 02:05:55,115
The ring is on my hand

1481
02:05:55,199 --> 02:05:59,830
And the wreath is on my brow

1482
02:05:59,913 --> 02:06:04,209
Satin and jewels grand

1483
02:06:04,960 --> 02:06:10,299
Are all at my command

1484
02:06:10,383 --> 02:06:16,472
And I am happy now

1485
02:06:20,769 --> 02:06:25,232
And my lord, he loves me well

1486
02:06:25,315 --> 02:06:29,153
But when first he breathed his vow

1487
02:06:29,236 --> 02:06:33,199
I felt my bosom swell

1488
02:06:33,283 --> 02:06:37,620
For the words rang as a knell

1489
02:06:37,704 --> 02:06:41,875
And the voice seemed his who fell

1490
02:06:41,958 --> 02:06:46,172
In the battle down the dell

1491
02:06:46,255 --> 02:06:52,094
And who is happy now

1492
02:06:54,431 --> 02:06:58,727
But he spoke to reassure me

1493
02:06:58,810 --> 02:07:02,981
And he kissed my pallid brow

1494
02:07:03,064 --> 02:07:06,903
While a reverie came o'er me

1495
02:07:07,862 --> 02:07:11,240
And to the churchyard bore me

1496
02:07:11,324 --> 02:07:15,245
And I sighed to him before me

1497
02:07:16,079 --> 02:07:19,583
Thinking him dead D'Elormie

1498
02:07:19,708 --> 02:07:24,755
"Oh, I am happy now!"

1499
02:07:45,528 --> 02:07:47,656
Ah...

1500
02:08:02,088 --> 02:08:07,635
And I am happy now

1501
02:08:10,097 --> 02:08:14,476
And thus the words were spoken

1502
02:08:14,560 --> 02:08:18,397
And this the plighted vow

1503
02:08:18,522 --> 02:08:22,402
And though my faith be broken

1504
02:08:22,485 --> 02:08:26,906
And though my heart be broken

1505
02:08:26,990 --> 02:08:31,035
Here is a ring, as token

1506
02:08:31,120 --> 02:08:36,792
That I am happy now

1507
02:08:39,461 --> 02:08:43,925
Would God I could awaken

1508
02:08:44,009 --> 02:08:47,429
For I dream I know not how

1509
02:08:47,554 --> 02:08:51,933
And my soul is sorely shaken

1510
02:08:52,017 --> 02:08:55,938
Lest an evil step be taken

1511
02:08:56,022 --> 02:09:00,485
Lest the dead who is forsaken

1512
02:09:00,568 --> 02:09:06,116
May not be happy now

1513
02:09:09,203 --> 02:09:13,790
Ah...

